|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR             |:EX10001|16      |36          |
|2 |  └─MERGE OUTER JOIN             |        |16      |14          |
|3 |    ├─SORT                       |        |16      |7           |
|4 |    │ └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR    |        |16      |5           |
|5 |    │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |t1      |16      |5           |
|6 |    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |1       |6           |
|7 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)|:EX10000|1       |6           |
|8 |        └─TABLE GET              |t2      |1       |5           |
